metadata.name: Gorgon
metadata.description:
Gorgon features supernatural, unfamiliar creatures engaged in mysterious rituals, exploring themes of femininity and post-humanism, while satirizing symbols and representation of the archetypal female in mythology.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. Featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. 
Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.

PNG | AI + Digital Painting | 6024 × 6024
